Dialogue: 1,0:01:32.11,0:01:32.96,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,扳手腕
Dialogue: 1,0:01:38.25,0:01:39.12,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 1,0:01:39.42,0:01:42.04,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼西片那麼強啊
Dialogue: 1,0:01:43.60,0:01:46.18,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我每天都做俯臥撐啊
Dialogue: 1,0:01:47.13,0:01:49.32,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,一天大概做幾個啊
Dialogue: 1,0:01:51.28,0:01:53.47,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡的高木同學
Dialogue: 1,0:01:54.44,0:01:58.88,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,當天被高木同學捉弄次數的三倍
Dialogue: 1,0:01:58.89,0:02:00.57,Takagisan - text_cn_top,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡的高木同學
Dialogue: 1,0:02:03.54,0:02:04.74,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼說得出口啊
Dialogue: 1,0:02:05.19,0:02:06.67,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 就隨便做做啊
Dialogue: 1,0:02:06.77,0:02:09.44,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,看當天的狀態
Dialogue: 1,0:02:10.94,0:02:12.19,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 西片
Dialogue: 1,0:02:12.32,0:02:14.03,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來和我比比吧
Dialogue: 1,0:02:14.03,0:02:14.64,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 1,0:02:20.34,0:02:21.92,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,西片你真的很強啊
Dialogue: 1,0:02:24.19,0:02:25.51,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我來贏他
Dialogue: 1,0:02:35.37,0:02:35.96,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 1,0:02:41.46,0:02:43.06,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,又被留下來打掃衛生了？
Dialogue: 1,0:02:43.41,0:02:44.17,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 是啊
Dialogue: 1,0:02:44.76,0:02:46.72,Takagisan - text_cn_top,NTP,0,0,0,,這還不是你害的
Dialogue: 1,0:02:47.55,0:02:49.26,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,西片 你這小子
Dialogue: 1,0:02:49.50,0:02:50.81,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,對…對不起
Dialogue: 1,0:02:57.97,0:02:59.61,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,有…有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:03:02.04,0:03:03.60,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你在幹嘛啊 高木同學
Dialogue: 1,0:03:03.80,0:03:05.97,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,西片 你把椅子搬過來一下
Dialogue: 1,0:03:06.30,0:03:06.75,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 1,0:03:10.85,0:03:12.39,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,這怎麼回事啊 高木同學…
Dialogue: 1,0:03:12.47,0:03:15.21,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,要比一比嗎 扳手腕
Dialogue: 1,0:03:18.74,0:03:20.60,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不是很強 可以哦
Dialogue: 1,0:03:21.70,0:03:24.73,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那輸了的要請客喝果汁哦
Dialogue: 1,0:03:26.26,0:03:30.21,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,高木同學 你不知道我扳手腕很厲害吧
Dialogue: 1,0:03:30.64,0:03:33.91,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直堅持在做被你捉弄次數乘以三倍的俯臥撐
Dialogue: 1,0:03:34.29,0:03:37.17,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,男生裡面都沒幾個人能贏我吧
Dialogue: 1,0:03:37.82,0:03:41.38,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你就好好嚐嚐至今為止捉弄我的報應吧
Dialogue: 1,0:03:41.71,0:03:43.46,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那開始吧
Dialogue: 1,0:03:49.08,0:03:51.56,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我們剛才牽手了呢
Dialogue: 1,0:03:54.36,0:03:55.23,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 1,0:03:55.77,0:03:56.67,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼…
Dialogue: 1,0:03:57.49,0:04:00.22,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是覺得牽手很害羞嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:04:00.23,0:04:01.86,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不是啦
Dialogue: 1,0:04:08.53,0:04:13.17,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,好…好軟 簡直吹彈可破
Dialogue: 1,0:04:13.72,0:04:14.91,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,還有這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 1,0:04:15.09,0:04:17.26,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,一捏就會壞掉的纖細感
Dialogue: 1,0:04:17.91,0:04:18.76,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是…
Dialogue: 1,0:04:19.18,0:04:21.40,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,女孩子的手嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:04:21.92,0:04:23.56,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 西片
Dialogue: 1,0:04:23.63,0:04:24.74,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你手心出汗了哦
Dialogue: 1,0:04:26.69,0:04:28.20,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是在緊張
Dialogue: 1,0:04:28.50,0:04:29.90,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,明明我都不介意啊
Dialogue: 1,0:04:30.10,0:04:32.35,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎麼可能緊張啊
Dialogue: 1,0:04:34.26,0:04:34.91,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,再來一次
Dialogue: 1,0:04:36.68,0:04:38.97,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不要再胡思亂想了
Dialogue: 1,0:04:40.36,0:04:41.65,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那開始了哦
Dialogue: 1,0:04:42.34,0:04:43.07,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,預備
Dialogue: 1,0:04:43.23,0:04:43.69,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,開始
Dialogue: 1,0:04:51.93,0:04:54.37,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊 這麼弱的嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:05:02.68,0:05:04.11,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 1,0:05:04.62,0:05:08.11,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,是我變得太強了
Dialogue: 1,0:05:08.51,0:05:09.99,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,太高興了
Dialogue: 1,0:05:10.32,0:05:13.08,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,高木同學為了贏我竟然這麼拚命啊
Dialogue: 1,0:05:23.05,0:05:25.36,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 我贏啦
Dialogue: 1,0:05:28.93,0:05:31.66,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,大意了…一不小心就得意忘形了
Dialogue: 1,0:05:31.86,0:05:33.86,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,這場比賽我明明能贏的
Dialogue: 1,0:05:34.30,0:05:35.54,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我真是個傻子
Dialogue: 1,0:05:37.20,0:05:38.24,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,要再比一次嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:05:40.11,0:05:40.71,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,請務必
Dialogue: 1,0:05:43.88,0:05:46.69,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不要以為同樣的手段能奏效兩次
Dialogue: 1,0:05:46.85,0:05:48.32,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,高木同學 天真
Dialogue: 1,0:05:48.39,0:05:49.59,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,太天真了
Dialogue: 1,0:05:50.10,0:05:51.89,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,這次要一開始就用全力
Dialogue: 1,0:05:52.06,0:05:54.07,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,讓你見識見識我的臂力吧
Dialogue: 1,0:05:57.25,0:05:57.88,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 1,0:05:59.53,0:06:00.00,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,今天
Dialogue: 1,0:06:01.47,0:06:02.83,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不如牽著手回家吧
Dialogue: 1,0:06:03.04,0:06:03.40,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 1,0:06:05.00,0:06:05.81,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你在說什麼…
Dialogue: 1,0:06:05.82,0:06:06.25,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,預備 開始
Dialogue: 1,0:06:14.79,0:06:16.32,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,又是我贏了哦
Dialogue: 1,0:06:20.99,0:06:21.93,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,要再來一次嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:06:23.32,0:06:24.94,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不了 算了吧
Dialogue: 1,0:06:25.61,0:06:26.44,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:06:28.23,0:06:31.15,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 我幫你一起打掃
Dialogue: 1,0:06:31.25,0:06:32.75,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,趕緊掃完回家吧
Dialogue: 1,0:06:36.79,0:06:39.09,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我居然輸給這麼纖細的小手
Dialogue: 1,0:06:39.66,0:06:41.93,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,黑板西片來擦
Dialogue: 1,0:06:42.07,0:06:43.53,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我去倒垃圾
Dialogue: 1,0:06:45.42,0:06:47.54,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,回去請我喝果汁哦
Dialogue: 1,0:06:59.16,0:07:01.09,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 出什麼事了嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:07:04.41,0:07:06.64,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不 沒有啊
Dialogue: 1,0:07:10.67,0:07:11.93,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,成熟
Dialogue: 1,0:07:13.65,0:07:15.37,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛…
Dialogue: 1,0:07:15.54,0:07:16.75,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,發生什麼了啊
Dialogue: 1,0:07:17.13,0:07:18.71,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛哦 早苗
Dialogue: 1,0:07:20.94,0:07:23.69,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是在想事情啦
Dialogue: 1,0:07:23.99,0:07:26.49,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,已經到初二了 要稍微成熟一點了
Dialogue: 1,0:07:28.24,0:07:28.74,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 1,0:07:29.30,0:07:31.77,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,初一初二都沒什麼區別吧
Dialogue: 1,0:07:34.64,0:07:35.40,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 1,0:07:36.39,0:07:41.39,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,前段時間那麼漂亮的櫻花都凋謝了
Dialogue: 1,0:07:43.75,0:07:46.55,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,花的生命真是轉瞬即逝啊
Dialogue: 1,0:07:47.25,0:07:49.59,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不過不只有花是這樣哦
Dialogue: 1,0:07:50.21,0:07:52.04,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,這個世界的所有事物
Dialogue: 1,0:07:52.36,0:07:55.98,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,全都 全都 全都是轉瞬即逝的哦
Dialogue: 1,0:07:56.09,0:07:56.83,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,比如？
Dialogue: 1,0:07:56.95,0:07:57.78,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,比如？
Dialogue: 1,0:08:00.10,0:08:02.29,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,比如說 沒錯
Dialogue: 1,0:08:02.51,0:08:06.07,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不管多好吃的蛋糕都是有保質期的
Dialogue: 1,0:08:06.87,0:08:09.72,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,糖也是舔著舔著就沒有了
Dialogue: 1,0:08:10.87,0:08:14.08,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是香蕉 放久了也會發黑變質
Dialogue: 1,0:08:14.26,0:08:15.53,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,全部都是食物…
Dialogue: 1,0:08:16.42,0:08:20.46,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,這個世界的所有事物都是既有始也有終的啊
Dialogue: 1,0:08:21.04,0:08:23.64,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,青春終有一天也會結束
Dialogue: 1,0:08:38.17,0:08:41.87,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不不 成熟完全不是這樣的好嘛
Dialogue: 1,0:08:44.32,0:08:48.04,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼看都像是鬧情緒的小孩啊 對吧
Dialogue: 1,0:08:48.85,0:08:50.67,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你在開什麼玩笑…
Dialogue: 1,0:08:55.82,0:08:56.89,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不…
Dialogue: 1,0:08:57.79,0:09:00.89,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的 很成熟 很成熟哦
Dialogue: 1,0:09:01.79,0:09:02.54,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嘛
Dialogue: 1,0:09:02.57,0:09:04.07,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 真的真的
Dialogue: 1,0:09:04.54,0:09:07.25,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,美奈真的很成熟呢
Dialogue: 1,0:09:07.62,0:09:09.44,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是真的嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:09:09.45,0:09:10.17,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,真的真的
Dialogue: 1,0:09:10.30,0:09:11.42,Takagisan - text_cn_top,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:09:10.15,0:09:10.76,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,真是孩子氣
Dialogue: 1,0:09:14.14,0:09:14.90,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,苦澀
Dialogue: 1,0:09:21.90,0:09:24.30,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,西片你可真有意思啊
Dialogue: 1,0:09:29.25,0:09:32.63,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,西片 說好了要請我喝果汁的對吧
Dialogue: 1,0:09:32.85,0:09:34.21,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…嗯…
Dialogue: 1,0:09:36.60,0:09:38.17,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,要喝什麼呢
Dialogue: 1,0:09:38.62,0:09:39.78,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,西片你決定好了嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:09:44.58,0:09:45.99,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是多好喝的果汁
Dialogue: 1,0:09:46.35,0:09:51.63,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,現在喝的果汁也只能嚐到扳手腕輸給高木同學的滋味
Dialogue: 1,0:09:59.17,0:09:59.79,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 1,0:10:00.84,0:10:01.72,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 1,0:10:04.63,0:10:06.35,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,喝什麼呢
Dialogue: 1,0:10:07.33,0:10:08.75,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不是這個
Dialogue: 1,0:10:09.52,0:10:12.40,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我想喝這個
Dialogue: 1,0:10:15.93,0:10:18.48,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 我有件事想問你們
Dialogue: 1,0:10:19.36,0:10:22.24,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,成熟到底是什麼
Dialogue: 1,0:10:24.66,0:10:26.71,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你是喜歡上北條同學了嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:10:28.15,0:10:33.35,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,因為很有名啊 她喜歡成熟的人這件事
Dialogue: 1,0:10:33.51,0:10:36.70,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜歡成熟的人
Dialogue: 1,0:10:37.90,0:10:39.18,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,和那個沒關係啦
Dialogue: 1,0:10:39.34,0:10:42.31,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是好奇成熟到底是什麼
Dialogue: 1,0:10:42.74,0:10:43.83,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嘛
Dialogue: 1,0:10:44.22,0:10:46.01,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,成熟嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:10:46.81,0:10:47.77,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,只要具備這個
Dialogue: 1,0:10:47.93,0:10:50.27,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,或許就不會被高木同學捉弄了
Dialogue: 1,0:10:50.76,0:10:51.55,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想知道
Dialogue: 1,0:10:52.24,0:10:53.14,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 1,0:10:53.15,0:10:55.14,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,西片也喜歡上北條同學了嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:10:55.42,0:10:57.56,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不 西片喜歡的是高木同學吧
Dialogue: 1,0:10:57.62,0:10:59.83,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不不 完全不是
Dialogue: 1,0:11:00.83,0:11:03.46,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 說起成熟
Dialogue: 1,0:11:03.56,0:11:05.33,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,果然還是那個吧
Dialogue: 1,0:11:05.42,0:11:06.00,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那個？
Dialogue: 1,0:11:06.10,0:11:07.31,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那個是什麼啊
Dialogue: 1,0:11:07.43,0:11:09.96,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,告訴我 告訴我吧 木村
Dialogue: 1,0:11:12.20,0:11:13.64,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那個當然是…
Dialogue: 1,0:11:16.80,0:11:18.69,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,咖啡
Dialogue: 1,0:11:21.54,0:11:23.72,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  那個是咖啡哦
Dialogue: 1,0:11:23.98,0:11:27.03,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 感覺今天就想喝這個
Dialogue: 1,0:11:27.13,0:11:28.61,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的能喝嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:11:28.65,0:11:30.82,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,西片你不是喝不了苦的嘛
Dialogue: 1,0:11:31.71,0:11:34.37,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你也只有現在能這麼說了
Dialogue: 1,0:11:35.31,0:11:38.10,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,每天早上我都有喝媽媽煮的咖啡
Dialogue: 1,0:11:38.22,0:11:41.80,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然不好喝 但也不是喝不了
Dialogue: 1,0:11:42.56,0:11:44.24,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,畏懼我的成熟吧
Dialogue: 1,0:11:44.29,0:11:46.18,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,以後別再捉弄我了
Dialogue: 1,0:11:48.74,0:11:49.41,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,好苦
Dialogue: 1,0:11:49.70,0:11:50.51,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 1,0:11:50.59,0:11:52.51,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,而且味道還這麼濃
Dialogue: 1,0:11:54.83,0:11:56.87,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,果然喝不了苦的啊
Dialogue: 1,0:11:58.01,0:11:59.93,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有啊 真好喝啊
Dialogue: 1,0:12:00.03,0:12:02.99,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺…怎麼說呢 人都變精神了呢
Dialogue: 1,0:12:06.29,0:12:07.16,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不接著喝了嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:12:07.23,0:12:07.80,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,要喝啊
Dialogue: 1,0:12:08.43,0:12:11.33,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 西片 你是不是出手汗了？
Dialogue: 1,0:12:11.78,0:12:15.15,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,才沒有 這是附在罐子上的水滴啦
Dialogue: 1,0:12:18.49,0:12:19.01,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 1,0:12:19.35,0:12:20.79,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 這麼說起來
Dialogue: 1,0:12:21.13,0:12:24.47,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我有在網上看到過「正確的咖啡品嘗方法」哦
Dialogue: 1,0:12:24.92,0:12:27.30,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,在嘴裡稍微含著一會的話
Dialogue: 1,0:12:27.56,0:12:29.56,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,就能充分感受到咖啡的味道呢
Dialogue: 1,0:12:29.66,0:12:33.44,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 要把這種東西暫時留在嘴裡？
Dialogue: 1,0:12:33.54,0:12:34.58,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不會吧
Dialogue: 1,0:12:36.92,0:12:38.84,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我有看到過這種謠言呢
Dialogue: 1,0:12:42.30,0:12:45.78,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 你也就只有現在能像這樣來捉弄我了
Dialogue: 1,0:12:46.00,0:12:48.70,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,快屈服在能喝光咖啡的我之下吧
Dialogue: 1,0:12:51.55,0:12:54.06,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼難嚥下去的話明明不用買的
Dialogue: 1,0:12:54.33,0:12:55.82,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不 很好喝啊
Dialogue: 1,0:12:56.44,0:12:59.81,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,高木同學也喝喝看吧 約好我請你的
Dialogue: 1,0:13:01.84,0:13:03.10,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,選你喜歡的吧
Dialogue: 1,0:13:03.87,0:13:04.63,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 1,0:13:06.27,0:13:07.73,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,要選什麼呢
Dialogue: 1,0:13:11.63,0:13:12.59,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那就這個
Dialogue: 1,0:13:20.35,0:13:22.44,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,蜜…蜜瓜蘇打
Dialogue: 1,0:13:25.09,0:13:26.27,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,好像很好喝
Dialogue: 1,0:13:26.75,0:13:27.38,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 1,0:13:28.75,0:13:30.05,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,要和我換著喝嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:13:42.81,0:13:45.95,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了 我喜歡喝咖啡
Dialogue: 1,0:13:52.40,0:13:53.68,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,總算是喝光了
Dialogue: 1,0:13:56.02,0:13:57.73,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,舌頭都麻了
Dialogue: 1,0:13:57.89,0:13:59.89,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 怎麼樣啊高木同學
Dialogue: 1,0:14:01.87,0:14:04.15,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,要喝一口蜜瓜蘇打嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:14:05.47,0:14:06.07,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 1,0:14:07.65,0:14:09.94,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不 但是…好想喝
Dialogue: 1,0:14:13.64,0:14:15.51,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,好想喝甜的東西
Dialogue: 1,0:14:15.94,0:14:19.33,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼…我就恭敬不如從命…
Dialogue: 1,0:14:19.58,0:14:20.94,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然是間接接吻
Dialogue: 1,0:14:22.13,0:14:24.53,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不 果然還是…
Dialogue: 1,0:14:25.83,0:14:29.00,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我還是再享受一下咖啡的餘韻吧
Dialogue: 1,0:14:32.98,0:14:33.56,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 1,0:14:35.25,0:14:38.77,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得就算能喝下咖啡也不算成熟哦
Dialogue: 1,0:14:41.22,0:14:44.14,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,早就被她看穿了
Dialogue: 1,0:14:44.69,0:14:47.47,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,而且就算西片變成熟了
Dialogue: 1,0:14:47.68,0:14:49.55,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我也會努力捉弄你的哦
Dialogue: 1,0:14:51.08,0:14:54.68,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,唉 等…真是的
Dialogue: 1,0:14:55.02,0:14:57.30,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,別在這種方面努力啊 高木同學
Dialogue: 1,0:14:58.53,0:15:00.46,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 笑什麼笑啦
Dialogue: 1,0:15:19.22,0:15:19.83,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,自行車
Dialogue: 1,0:15:44.90,0:15:46.95,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天真是太慘了
Dialogue: 1,0:15:47.92,0:15:51.32,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,今天能不能有什麼方法贏過高木同學呢
Dialogue: 1,0:15:51.56,0:15:52.09,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 1,0:15:52.96,0:15:53.71,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 1,0:15:54.31,0:15:56.18,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 早上好 高木同學
Dialogue: 1,0:15:56.63,0:15:57.49,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,一起走吧
Dialogue: 1,0:16:01.51,0:16:04.54,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事 感覺和平常不太一樣
Dialogue: 1,0:16:05.88,0:16:07.16,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,今天怎麼沒騎自行車？
Dialogue: 1,0:16:08.94,0:16:12.01,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,想和西片手牽手去上學 所以沒騎過來
Dialogue: 1,0:16:13.29,0:16:14.12,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你是這麼想的嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:16:14.23,0:16:15.98,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,完全沒有啦
Dialogue: 1,0:16:21.78,0:16:22.91,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡的高木同學
Dialogue: 1,0:16:22.95,0:16:24.15,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,一見面就捉弄我
Dialogue: 1,0:16:28.74,0:16:29.54,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這個
Dialogue: 1,0:16:29.76,0:16:30.84,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣肯定能行
Dialogue: 1,0:16:32.12,0:16:33.39,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,其實我的自行車…
Dialogue: 1,0:16:33.40,0:16:37.09,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,稍等一下 要是我能猜中你今天沒騎自行車來的理由
Dialogue: 1,0:16:37.11,0:16:38.84,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,就算我贏了 怎麼樣
Dialogue: 1,0:16:39.96,0:16:40.84,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,可以啊
Dialogue: 1,0:16:41.34,0:16:41.95,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 1,0:16:44.23,0:16:47.65,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天回家路上你隨口說出的那句話
Dialogue: 1,0:16:48.09,0:16:50.65,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺剎車不太靈了
Dialogue: 1,0:16:50.95,0:16:52.95,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我可沒聽漏哦
Dialogue: 1,0:16:53.84,0:16:55.81,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到這麼輕鬆就贏了
Dialogue: 1,0:16:55.81,0:16:57.36,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微有點掃興呢
Dialogue: 1,0:16:58.19,0:16:59.23,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,答案就是剎…
Dialogue: 1,0:16:59.28,0:16:59.97,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,稍等一下
Dialogue: 1,0:17:00.65,0:17:03.69,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,猜錯了的那一刻就是西片輸了哦
Dialogue: 1,0:17:05.10,0:17:05.66,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,答案是？
Dialogue: 1,0:17:09.44,0:17:10.82,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,等一會再告訴你
Dialogue: 1,0:17:10.98,0:17:11.65,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 1,0:17:59.26,0:17:59.88,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,快看 西片
Dialogue: 1,0:18:00.69,0:18:02.04,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,要走這邊試試嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:18:05.46,0:18:06.40,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,是可以啦
Dialogue: 1,0:18:10.78,0:18:14.14,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,台階 如果騎自行車的話就上不了台階
Dialogue: 1,0:18:14.77,0:18:16.69,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是為了走這條路？
Dialogue: 1,0:18:17.32,0:18:18.69,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,大概就是這樣了
Dialogue: 1,0:18:19.16,0:18:19.95,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,高木同學
Dialogue: 1,0:18:20.05,0:18:20.57,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 1,0:18:29.96,0:18:32.65,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不…沒什麼
Dialogue: 1,0:18:34.87,0:18:37.99,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,要慎重點 再思考一下吧
Dialogue: 1,0:18:40.11,0:18:44.16,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有自行車就能走和平常不一樣的路上學了 好開心啊
Dialogue: 1,0:18:44.56,0:18:46.75,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,果然不是嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:18:49.82,0:18:54.23,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,這條路上常有附近的孩子們在地上畫畫哦
Dialogue: 1,0:18:55.65,0:18:56.60,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,比如呢
Dialogue: 1,0:18:57.44,0:18:58.85,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你看 有了有了
Dialogue: 1,0:19:05.17,0:19:07.49,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,來玩跳格子吧
Dialogue: 1,0:19:07.89,0:19:09.56,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,一一 二
Dialogue: 1,0:19:10.50,0:19:12.44,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,一二一二
Dialogue: 1,0:19:12.49,0:19:14.26,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,一一二
Dialogue: 1,0:19:15.21,0:19:19.09,Takagisan - text_cn_top,NTP,0,0,0,,一二一二一一二
Dialogue: 1,0:19:16.97,0:19:19.60,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,高木同學也還是個小孩子呢
Dialogue: 1,0:19:21.60,0:19:25.98,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有自行車就能玩跳格子了 真開心呢
Dialogue: 1,0:19:27.64,0:19:32.47,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,高木同學已經預料到這裡有跳格子的塗鴉了
Dialogue: 1,0:19:33.04,0:19:35.64,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有自行車的話她自己就能玩耍了
Dialogue: 1,0:19:35.96,0:19:36.63,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才
Dialogue: 1,0:19:37.02,0:19:38.93,Takagisan - text_cn_top,NTP,0,0,0,,一一二
Dialogue: 1,0:19:37.39,0:19:39.18,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不不不 我不能著急
Dialogue: 1,0:19:39.47,0:19:40.98,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,猜錯就輸了啊
Dialogue: 1,0:19:39.88,0:19:41.54,Takagisan - text_cn_top,NTP,0,0,0,,一一二
Dialogue: 1,0:19:42.12,0:19:43.00,Takagisan - text_cn_top,NTP,0,0,0,,一二
Dialogue: 1,0:19:41.94,0:19:43.75,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,要深思熟慮才行
Dialogue: 1,0:19:44.66,0:19:46.30,Takagisan - text_cn_top,NTP,0,0,0,,一一二
Dialogue: 1,0:19:47.46,0:19:48.95,Takagisan - text_cn_top,NTP,0,0,0,,一一二
Dialogue: 1,0:19:45.72,0:19:49.46,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,高木同學 我感覺這場比賽不公平啊
Dialogue: 1,0:19:50.69,0:19:51.33,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 1,0:19:51.74,0:19:57.07,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,因為就算我猜對了 只要你說猜錯我就輸了
Dialogue: 1,0:19:58.69,0:20:02.26,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,沒問題的哦 我不會對西片你說謊的
Dialogue: 1,0:20:02.77,0:20:03.84,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:20:06.02,0:20:06.90,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,是貓啊
Dialogue: 1,0:20:07.25,0:20:08.34,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊也有哦
Dialogue: 1,0:20:09.70,0:20:11.78,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,這條路上有很多貓的哦
Dialogue: 1,0:20:15.36,0:20:17.06,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,來 來 怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: 1,0:20:20.54,0:20:23.21,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,高木同學 我可以說答案了嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:20:23.81,0:20:25.32,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 你請
Dialogue: 1,0:20:25.60,0:20:29.28,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,今天你不是騎自行車而是走路上學的理由
Dialogue: 1,0:20:29.34,0:20:30.34,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是
Dialogue: 1,0:20:31.08,0:20:32.61,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,剎車故障了
Dialogue: 1,0:20:34.32,0:20:38.15,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,台階 跳格子遊戲 然後還有貓
Dialogue: 1,0:20:39.45,0:20:43.37,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然是想讓我覺得這些都是騎車做不到的事情
Dialogue: 1,0:20:43.69,0:20:46.31,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,但似乎有點太刻意了呢
Dialogue: 1,0:20:46.93,0:20:52.81,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,想讓我的注意點離開你昨天不經意說出的剎車的違和感上
Dialogue: 1,0:20:52.82,0:20:54.08,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你的目的已經暴露無遺了
Dialogue: 1,0:20:54.51,0:20:55.92,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣啊高木同學
Dialogue: 1,0:20:56.04,0:20:58.57,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,答對了還是答錯了
Dialogue: 1,0:20:59.15,0:20:59.77,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,答錯了
Dialogue: 1,0:21:04.56,0:21:09.61,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,答案是想要看到想猜中我為什麼沒有騎自行車
Dialogue: 1,0:21:09.66,0:21:13.15,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,因此而各種苦惱的西片呢
Dialogue: 1,0:21:15.93,0:21:16.87,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:21:17.22,0:21:19.91,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,真的啊 是西片你輸了
Dialogue: 1,0:21:21.09,0:21:23.91,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,在我發起挑戰的時候就已經…
Dialogue: 1,0:21:24.00,0:21:27.70,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,真是遺憾啊 明明我準備了兩個答案
Dialogue: 1,0:21:28.05,0:21:32.12,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,兩個？兩個是指還有其他正確答案嗎？
Dialogue: 1,0:21:32.23,0:21:32.72,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 1,0:21:33.48,0:21:35.42,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,另一個答案是什麼啊
Dialogue: 1,0:21:38.60,0:21:41.48,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得西片你猜不到哦
Dialogue: 1,0:21:42.13,0:21:43.24,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那算什麼啦
Dialogue: 1,0:21:43.30,0:21:45.60,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,反正西片已經輸了 無所謂啦
Dialogue: 1,0:21:45.79,0:21:47.90,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,唉 告訴我啦
Dialogue: 1,0:21:49.10,0:21:50.13,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: 1,0:21:50.45,0:21:51.66,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼這樣…
Dialogue: 1,0:21:53.10,0:21:54.43,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我很在意啊
Dialogue: 1,0:21:57.20,0:21:59.10,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我最開始就告訴你了
Dialogue: 1,0:21:59.22,0:22:00.37,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 你說了什麼嗎？
Dialogue: 1,0:22:01.31,0:22:02.62,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼都沒有
Dialogue: 1,0:22:02.80,0:22:04.69,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,告訴我啦西片同學
Dialogue: 1,0:22:05.24,0:22:06.77,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼啦
Dialogue: 1,0:22:06.87,0:22:08.45,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能沒什麼的吧
Dialogue: 1,0:22:08.46,0:22:09.47,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,就是沒什麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.11,0:01:32.96,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,腕ずもう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.25,0:01:39.12,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,くそ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.42,0:01:42.04,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,西片 なんで そんなに強いんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.60,0:01:46.18,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,まあ 毎日 腕立てをやってるからね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.13,0:01:49.32,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,1日何回くらい  やってるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.28,0:01:53.47,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,高木さんめ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.44,0:01:58.88,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,その日   高木さんに  からかわれた回数×3回
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.89,0:02:00.57,Takagisan - text_jp_top,,0,0,0,,高木さんめ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.54,0:02:04.74,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,なんて言えるか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.19,0:02:06.67,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,まあ 適当だね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.77,0:02:09.44,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,その日のコンディションに  よるっていうか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.94,0:02:12.19,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,おい 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.32,0:02:14.03,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,次は俺とやろうぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.03,0:02:14.64,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,うん いいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.34,0:02:21.92,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,ホント強いな 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.19,0:02:25.51,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,俺が勝ってやる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.37,0:02:35.96,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.46,0:02:43.06,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,また居残り掃除?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.41,0:02:44.17,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,まあね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.76,0:02:46.72,Takagisan - text_jp_top,,0,0,0,,誰のせいだと思ってるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.55,0:02:49.26,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,西片 こら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.50,0:02:50.81,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,す… すみません
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.97,0:02:59.61,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,な… 何か用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.04,0:03:03.60,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,何してんの  高木さん
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.80,0:03:05.97,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,西片 イス持ってきて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.30,0:03:06.75,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,えっ?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.85,0:03:12.39,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,どういうこと  高木…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.47,0:03:15.21,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,勝負しない  腕ずもう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.74,0:03:20.60,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,あんまり強くないけど いいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.70,0:03:24.73,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,じゃあ 負けたほうが  ジュースおごるってことで
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.26,0:03:30.21,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,高木さん  俺が腕ずもう強いことを  知らないんだな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.64,0:03:33.91,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,からかわれた回数×3回の腕立てを  やってきたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.29,0:03:37.17,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,男子でも 俺に勝てるヤツは  ほとんどいないだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.82,0:03:41.38,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,今まで俺を からかってきた報いを  受けるがいい
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.71,0:03:43.46,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,じゃあ 始めようか
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.08,0:03:51.56,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,手 つないだよね さっき
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.36,0:03:55.23,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,どうしたの
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.77,0:03:56.67,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,い… いや…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.49,0:04:00.22,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,もしかして  手つなぐの恥ずかしいの
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.23,0:04:01.86,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,ち… 違うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.53,0:04:13.17,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,や… 柔らかい  フニフニしている
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.72,0:04:14.91,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,それに何だ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.09,0:04:17.26,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,この頼りない骨の細工
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.91,0:04:18.76,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,これが…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.18,0:04:21.40,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,女の子の… 手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.92,0:04:23.56,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,あれ  西片
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.63,0:04:24.74,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,手汗かいてるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.69,0:04:28.20,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,もしかして緊張してる
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.50,0:04:29.90,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,別に気にしないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.10,0:04:32.35,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,き… 緊張なんて  するわけないだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.26,0:04:34.91,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,もう一度
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.68,0:04:38.97,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,もう余計なことは考えるな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.36,0:04:41.65,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,じゃあ いくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.34,0:04:43.07,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,用意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.23,0:04:43.69,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,ドン
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.93,0:04:54.37,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,何だ  この弱さは
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.68,0:05:04.11,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,そうか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.62,0:05:08.11,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,俺が強くなりすぎてしまったのだな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.51,0:05:09.99,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,なんて楽しいんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.32,0:05:13.08,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,高木さんが 俺に勝とうと  必死じゃないか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.05,0:05:25.36,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,やった  勝った
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.93,0:05:31.66,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,油断してしまった  つい楽しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.86,0:05:33.86,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,勝てる勝負だったのに
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.30,0:05:35.54,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,俺のバカ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.20,0:05:38.24,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,もう1回やる
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.11,0:05:40.71,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,ぜひ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.88,0:05:46.69,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,2度も あんな手が通用すると  思っているのか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.85,0:05:48.32,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,高木さんめ 甘い
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.39,0:05:49.59,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,甘すぎるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.10,0:05:51.89,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,最初から全力でいく
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.06,0:05:54.07,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,俺の筋力を食らえ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.25,0:05:57.88,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,なに
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.53,0:06:00.00,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,今日
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.47,0:06:02.83,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,手つないで帰ろっか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.04,0:06:03.40,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,は?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.00,0:06:05.81,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,な… 何を…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.82,0:06:06.25,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,用意 ドン
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.79,0:06:16.32,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,また私の勝ちだね
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.99,0:06:21.93,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,もう1回する
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.32,0:06:24.94,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,, いや いいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.61,0:06:26.44,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,そっか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.23,0:06:31.15,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,さてと  掃除 手伝うから
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.25,0:06:32.75,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,早く終わらせて帰ろうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.79,0:06:39.09,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,こんな細い手に負けるなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.66,0:06:41.93,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,黒板は西片担当ね
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.07,0:06:43.53,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,私はゴミ捨ててくる
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.42,0:06:47.54,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,帰り ジュースおごってね
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.16,0:07:01.09,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,どうしたの  何かあった
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.41,0:07:06.64,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,いや  別に
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.67,0:07:11.93,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,大人っぽく
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.65,0:07:15.37,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,いたたた…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.54,0:07:16.75,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,何かあったの
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.13,0:07:18.71,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,痛いよ サナエちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.94,0:07:23.69,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,ちょっと物思いにふけってみたの
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.99,0:07:26.49,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,もう中2だし 大人っぽく
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.24,0:07:28.74,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,はあ?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.30,0:07:31.77,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,中1も中2も変わらないと思う
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.64,0:07:35.40,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,ほら
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.39,0:07:41.39,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,つい こないだまで あんなに きれいだった桜の花も  散っちゃったでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.75,0:07:46.55,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,花って はかないなって
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.25,0:07:49.59,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,でも それは花だけじゃないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.21,0:07:52.04,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,この世界のあらゆるもの
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.36,0:07:55.98,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,みんな みんな み〜んな はかない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.09,0:07:56.83,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,例えば?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.95,0:07:57.78,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,例えば?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.10,0:08:02.29,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,た… 例えば… そう
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.51,0:08:06.07,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,どんなに おいしいケーキにだって  賞味期限があるし
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.87,0:08:09.72,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,アメも なめてるうちに  なくなってしまう
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.87,0:08:14.08,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,バナナだって  放っとくと黒ずんできちゃう
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.26,0:08:15.53,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,全部 食べ物…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.42,0:08:20.46,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,この世の全てには  始まりがあって 終わりがあるよね
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.04,0:08:23.64,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,青春だって いつかは終わっちゃう
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.17,0:08:41.87,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,いやいや  大人っぽくって  全然 そんな感じしないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.32,0:08:48.04,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,どう見ても  ご機嫌斜めな子供だって
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.85,0:08:50.67,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,一体 何の冗談…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.82,0:08:56.89,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,い… いや…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.79,0:09:00.89,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,いや 大人っぽい  大人っぽかった
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.79,0:09:02.54,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,ホント
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.57,0:09:04.07,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,うん ホント ホント
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.54,0:09:07.25,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,いや ミナはホント大人っぽいな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.62,0:09:09.44,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,ホントにホント
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.45,0:09:10.17,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,ホント ホント
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.30,0:09:11.42,Takagisan - text_jp_top,,0,0,0,,ねえ ホント
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.15,0:09:10.76,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,子供
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.14,0:09:14.90,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,にがみ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.90,0:09:24.30,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,西片ってホント面白いねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.25,0:09:32.63,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,西片　ジュースおごってくれる  約束だったよね
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.85,0:09:34.21,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,あっ うん…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.60,0:09:38.17,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,何にしよっかな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.62,0:09:39.78,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,西片は決めた
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.58,0:09:45.99,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,どんなに おいしくても
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.35,0:09:51.63,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,今飲むジュースは  高木さんに  腕ずもうで負けた敗北の味
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.17,0:09:59.79,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,どうしたの
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.84,0:10:01.72,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,別に
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.63,0:10:06.35,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,何にしよっかな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.33,0:10:08.75,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,いや 違うな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.52,0:10:12.40,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,今日は これの気分だな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.93,0:10:18.48,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,なあ ちょっと聞きたいんだけどさ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.36,0:10:22.24,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,大人っぽいって 何だと思う
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.66,0:10:26.71,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,北条さん狙ってんの
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.15,0:10:33.35,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,だって 有名だぜ  タイプは大人っぽい人だ”って
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.51,0:10:36.70,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,私 大人っぽい人が好き
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.90,0:10:39.18,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,いや 関係ねえから
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.34,0:10:42.31,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,大人っぽいって何なのか  気になっただけだっての
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.74,0:10:43.83,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,ホントか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.22,0:10:46.01,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,大人っぽさか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.81,0:10:47.77,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,それがあれば
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.93,0:10:50.27,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,高木さんに  からかわれなくなるかも
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.76,0:10:51.55,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,俺も知りたい
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.24,0:10:53.14,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,な〜んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.15,0:10:55.14,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,西片も北条さん狙い
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.42,0:10:57.56,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,いや　西片は高木さんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.62,0:10:59.83,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,いやいや 全然 違うから
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.83,0:11:03.46,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,まあ 大人っぽさっていったらさ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.56,0:11:05.33,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,やっぱ あれじゃねえかな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.42,0:11:06.00,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,“あれ”?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.10,0:11:07.31,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,“あれ”って 何だ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.43,0:11:09.96,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,教えてよ  教えてくれよ 木村
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.20,0:11:13.64,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,それは…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.80,0:11:18.69,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,“コーシー”だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.54,0:11:23.72,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,あれ  それ コーヒーだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.98,0:11:27.03,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,ああ  なんか今日 そんな気分でね
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.13,0:11:28.61,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,ホントに飲めるの
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.65,0:11:30.82,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,西片 苦いの苦手でしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.71,0:11:34.37,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,そんなこと言ってられるのも  今のうちだぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.31,0:11:38.10,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,前に 朝食で  母さんが出したコーヒー
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.22,0:11:41.80,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,おいしくはなかったが  飲めないほどじゃなかったんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.56,0:11:44.24,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,俺の大人っぽさにビビれ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.29,0:11:46.18,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,そして もう からかうなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.74,0:11:49.41,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,にがっ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.70,0:11:50.51,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,何だこれ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.59,0:11:52.51,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,それに すごい においが
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.83,0:11:56.87,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,やっぱり苦手なんじゃないの
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.01,0:11:59.93,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,いや  うまいな
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.03,0:12:02.99,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,なんか この… 目の覚める感じがさ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.29,0:12:07.16,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,飲まないの
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.23,0:12:07.80,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,飲むけど
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.43,0:12:11.33,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,あれ  西片 手汗かいてない?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.78,0:12:15.15,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,かいてないよ  これは缶についてた水滴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.49,0:12:19.01,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,よし
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.35,0:12:20.79,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,あっ  そういえば
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.13,0:12:24.47,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,ネットで  “正しいコーヒーの味わい方”  って見たことあってね
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.92,0:12:27.30,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,“口の中で しばらく転がすと
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.56,0:12:29.56,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,においが感じられて いい”って
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.66,0:12:33.44,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,えっ  こんなものを  口の中に しばらく置いとく?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.54,0:12:34.58,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,ウソだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.92,0:12:38.84,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,そういうデマを見たことあるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.30,0:12:45.78,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,くそ… そんなふうに  からかえるのも今のうちだぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.00,0:12:48.70,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,コーヒーを飲み干す俺に  ひれ伏すがいい
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.55,0:12:54.06,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,そんなに苦手なら  買わなきゃいいのに
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.33,0:12:55.82,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,いや おいしくてさ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.44,0:12:59.81,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,高木さんも飲んだら  約束だから おごってあげるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.84,0:13:03.10,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,好きな物選んで
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.87,0:13:04.63,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.27,0:13:07.73,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,何にしよっかな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.63,0:13:12.59,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,じゃあ これ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.35,0:13:22.44,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,メ… メロンソーダ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.09,0:13:26.27,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,おいしそう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.75,0:13:27.38,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.75,0:13:30.05,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,交換してあげよっか
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.81,0:13:45.95,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,いや 俺 コーヒー好きだから
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.40,0:13:53.68,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,なんとか飲みきった
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.02,0:13:57.73,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,舌がビリビリする
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.89,0:13:59.89,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,でも どうだ  高木さん
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.87,0:14:04.15,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,メロンソーダ ひと口飲む
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.47,0:14:06.07,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,あれ?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.65,0:14:09.94,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,いや でも 欲しい…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.64,0:14:15.51,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,甘い物を飲みたい
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.94,0:14:19.33,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,じゃ… じゃあ  せっかくだから もらおうかな
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.58,0:14:20.94,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,間接キスだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.13,0:14:24.53,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,いや やっぱり…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.83,0:14:29.00,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,コーヒーの後味を楽しむかな
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.98,0:14:33.56,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.25,0:14:38.77,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,コーヒーを飲めても  別に大人っぽくないと思うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.22,0:14:44.14,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,とっくに見抜かれていた
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.69,0:14:47.47,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,それに 西片が大人っぽくなっても
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.68,0:14:49.55,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,私は頑張って からかうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.08,0:14:54.68,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,えっ… あっ ちょ…   もう
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.02,0:14:57.30,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,そこは頑張らないでよ 高木さん
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.53,0:15:00.46,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,もう 笑ってばっかで
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.22,0:15:19.83,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,自転車
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.90,0:15:46.95,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,昨日も さんざんだった
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.92,0:15:51.32,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,今日こそ 何か高木さんに  勝てるものはないか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.56,0:15:52.09,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.96,0:15:53.71,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,おはよう
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.31,0:15:56.18,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,あ  おはよう 高木さん
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.63,0:15:57.49,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,一緒に行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.51,0:16:04.54,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,何だ  いつもと感じが違うような
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.88,0:16:07.16,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,今日 自転車は?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.94,0:16:12.01,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,西片と手つないで  学校行きたくて 置いてきた
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.29,0:16:14.12,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,…と思う
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.23,0:16:15.98,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,思わないよ 全然
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.78,0:16:22.91,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,高木さんめ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.95,0:16:24.15,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,すぐこれだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.74,0:16:29.54,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,これだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.76,0:16:30.84,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,これでいけるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.12,0:16:33.39,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,実は 自転車…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.40,0:16:37.09,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,ちょっと待って 今日 自転車じゃない理由  当てられたら
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.11,0:16:38.84,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,俺の勝ちってのは どう
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.96,0:16:40.84,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,いいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.34,0:16:41.95,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,よし
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.23,0:16:47.65,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,昨日 帰り道で  チラッと言っていた あのセリフ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.09,0:16:50.65,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,なんかブレーキの利きが悪いな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.95,0:16:52.95,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,俺は聞き逃してないのだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.84,0:16:55.81,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,こうも あっさり勝てるとは
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.81,0:16:57.36,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,少し拍子抜けだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.19,0:16:59.23,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,答えは ブレ…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.28,0:16:59.97,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,ちょっと待って
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.65,0:17:03.69,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,間違ったら  その時点で西片の負けだからね
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.10,0:17:05.66,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,答えは?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.44,0:17:10.82,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,もうちょっと あとで…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.98,0:17:11.65,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,そう
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.26,0:17:59.88,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,ねえ 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.69,0:18:02.04,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,こっちから行ってみない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.46,0:18:06.40,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,いいけど
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.78,0:18:14.14,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,階段  自転車だと階段はムリ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.77,0:18:16.69,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,このルートを通るために?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.32,0:18:18.69,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,多分 それだな
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.16,0:18:19.95,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,高木さん
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.05,0:18:20.57,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,うん?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.96,0:18:32.65,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,いや 何でもない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.87,0:18:37.99,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,ここは慎重に もう少し考えよう
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.11,0:18:44.16,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,自転車ないと  いつもと違う道通れて 楽しいな
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.56,0:18:46.75,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,やはり 違うのか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.82,0:18:54.23,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,この道 近所の子供たちが  よく地面に絵とか描いてるんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.65,0:18:56.60,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,例えばね
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.44,0:18:58.85,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,ほら  あったあった
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.17,0:19:07.49,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,けんぱ遊び やってみようっと
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.89,0:19:09.56,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,けんけん ぱ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.50,0:19:12.44,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,けん ぱ  けん ぱ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.49,0:19:14.26,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,けんけん ぱ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.21,0:19:19.09,Takagisan - text_jp_top,,0,0,0,,けん ぱ  けん ぱ   けんけん ぱ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.97,0:19:19.60,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,高木さんも  まだまだ お子ちゃまだな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.60,0:19:25.98,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,自転車ないと  けんぱ遊びできて ホント楽しいな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.64,0:19:32.47,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,高木さんは この道に けんぱ遊びの  落書きがあることを予想していた
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.04,0:19:35.64,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,自転車がなければ 自分も遊べる
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.96,0:19:36.63,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,だから
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.02,0:19:38.93,Takagisan - text_jp_top,,0,0,0,,けんけん ぱ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.39,0:19:39.18,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,いやいや　焦るな 俺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.47,0:19:40.98,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,間違ったら負けなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.88,0:19:41.54,Takagisan - text_jp_top,,0,0,0,,けんけん ぱ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.12,0:19:43.00,Takagisan - text_jp_top,,0,0,0,,けん ぱ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.94,0:19:43.75,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,じっくり考えて
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.66,0:19:46.30,Takagisan - text_jp_top,,0,0,0,,けんけん ぱ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.46,0:19:48.95,Takagisan - text_jp_top,,0,0,0,,けんけん ぱ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.72,0:19:49.46,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,高木さん  この勝負  公平じゃない気がするんだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.69,0:19:51.33,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,なんで?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.74,0:19:57.07,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,だって 正解しても 高木さんが“違う”って言ったら 俺の負けになっちゃうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.69,0:20:02.26,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,大丈夫だよ  私 西片にはウソつかないから
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.77,0:20:03.84,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,ホントかな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.02,0:20:06.90,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,猫だ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.25,0:20:08.34,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,こっちにもいるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.70,0:20:11.78,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,この道 猫多いんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.36,0:20:17.06,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,おいおい  どうだ おい
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.54,0:20:23.21,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,高木さん  答えを言ってもいいかな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.81,0:20:25.32,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,うん  どうぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.60,0:20:29.28,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,今日 自転車ではなく  歩いて登校している理由
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.34,0:20:30.34,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,それは
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.08,0:20:32.61,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,ブレーキの故障
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.32,0:20:38.15,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,階段 けんぱ遊び  そして 猫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.45,0:20:43.37,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,自転車にはできないことに  意識を向けようとしたみたいだが
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.69,0:20:46.31,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,少し やりすぎてしまったようだね
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.93,0:20:52.81,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,昨日 思わず  口に出してしまった—ブレーキの違和感から 俺の思考を  遠ざけようとしているのが
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.82,0:20:54.08,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,バレバレだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.51,0:20:55.92,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,どうだい  高木さん
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.04,0:20:58.57,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,正解か 不正解か
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.15,0:20:59.77,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,不正解
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.56,0:21:09.61,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,正解は “なぜ私が自転車じゃないのか  その理由を当てようとして”
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.66,0:21:13.15,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,“あれこれ悩んでいる西片を  見たいから”でした
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.93,0:21:16.87,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,ホントに
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.22,0:21:19.91,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,ホントだよ  西片の負け
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.09,0:21:23.91,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,俺が勝負を  仕掛けるところから 既に…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.00,0:21:27.70,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,残念だったね  答え 2つも用意しといたのに
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.05,0:21:32.12,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,2つ?  2つって…別の正解があるってこと?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.23,0:21:32.72,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.48,0:21:35.42,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,もう1この答えって 何だったの
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.60,0:21:41.48,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,西片には当てられないと思うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.13,0:21:43.24,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,何それ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.30,0:21:45.60,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,西片の負けだし もういいでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.79,0:21:47.90,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,えっ  教えてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.10,0:21:50.13,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,さあね
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.45,0:21:51.66,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,そんな…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.10,0:21:54.43,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,気になるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.20,0:21:59.10,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,最初に言ったんだけどな
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.22,0:22:00.37,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,えっ なに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.31,0:22:02.62,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,何でもないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.80,0:22:04.69,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,お… 教えてよ 高木さん
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.24,0:22:06.77,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,何でもないって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.87,0:22:08.45,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,何でもないわけないでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.46,0:22:09.47,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,何でもないもん
